REACTION   (35-BR-79(N,G)35-BR-80-M,,SIG)
DECAY-DATA (35-BR-80-M,4.5HR,B-)
ANALYSIS   Decay of 35-Br-80 second metastable state (H-life =
            4.5 hr) to the ground state (H-life = 18 min) by
            isomeric transition was considered in analysis of the
            observed radiations.
COMMENT    By compiler. The H-life values given by Lederer,et al.,
            Table of Isotopes,6th ed. are 17.6 min for ground and
            4.38 hr for the second metastable state. Transition
            from the 4.38-hr to the 17.6-min state proceeds via a
            7.4 nanosec state which should not affect the analysis
