REACTION   (35-BR-81(N,G)35-BR-82,,SIG)
RAD-DET    (35-BR-82,B-)
COMMENT    By compiler. Lederer,et al.,Table of Isotopes,6th ed.,
            show a metastable state (half-life = 6.1 min) for 82Br
            which decays about 99% by isomeric transition to
            the ground state (half-life = 35.34 hr) and less than
            1% by beta- emission. The authors observed radiation
            of 36 hr half-life and do not mention the metastable
            state.
           Therefore the tabulated data probably represent the
            total capture cross section for Br-81(n,gamma)Br-82
HISTORY    (20260402A) VT. Original number expression restored.
