COMMENT    By compiler. Lederer et al.,Table of Isotopes, 6th ed.,
            show at metastable state (half-life = 18.7 min) in
            188Re which apparently decays entirely by isomeric
            transitions to the ground state (half-life = 16.7 hr).
            The authors do not mention the isomeric state.
            Therefore the tabulated data probably represent the
            total capture cross section for production of 188Rh
            by the reaction 187Re(n,gamma)188Re.
